<subSubSection pageId="13" pageNumber="38" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="13.[151,1436,258,508]" pageId="13" pageNumber="38">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[196,360,370,396]" pageId="13" pageNumber="38">Distribution.</emphasis>
First record of 
<taxonomicName box="[551,855,370,395]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Macrouridae" genus="Squalogadus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gadiformes" pageId="13" pageNumber="38" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="modificatus">
<emphasis box="[551,855,370,395]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="38">Squalogadus modificatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the WSA. Collected from off Bahia, Espírito Santo and Rio de Janeiro, at depths from 
<quantity box="[632,819,408,434]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.6355" metricValueMax="1.9289999999999998" metricValueMin="1.3419999999999999" pageId="13" pageNumber="38" unit="m" value="1635.5" valueMax="1929.0" valueMin="1342.0">
<date box="[632,787,408,434]" pageId="13" pageNumber="38" value="1342" valueMax="1929">1342 to 1929</date>
m
</quantity>
. It was described from off Kyushu, 
<collectingCountry box="[1237,1304,408,434]" name="Japan" pageId="13" pageNumber="38">Japan</collectingCountry>
(
<geoCoordinate box="[1320,1431,408,434]" direction="north" orientation="latitude" pageId="13" pageNumber="38" precision="925" value="32.533333">
<number box="[1320,1353,408,434]" pageId="13" pageNumber="38" value="32.0">32</number>
° 
<number box="[1363,1396,408,434]" pageId="13" pageNumber="38" value="32.0">32</number>
’ N
</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate box="[151,284,445,471]" direction="west" orientation="longitude" pageId="13" pageNumber="38" precision="925" value="-132.41667">
<number box="[151,199,445,471]" pageId="13" pageNumber="38" value="132.0">132</number>
° 
<number box="[209,241,445,471]" pageId="13" pageNumber="38" value="25.0">25</number>
’ W
</geoCoordinate>
), and is known to have a wide distribution throughout the North Atlantic and Pacific (
<bibRefCitation author="Geistdoerfer" pageId="13" pageNumber="45" refString="Geistdoerfer, P. (1990) Macrouridae. In: Quero, J. C., Hureau, J. C., Karrer, C., Post, A. &amp; Saldanha, L. (Eds.) Check-list of the fishes of the eastern tropical Atlantic (CLOFETA). JNICT, Lisbon; SEI, Paris; and UNESCO, Paris. Vol. 2. pp. 541 - 563." type="book chapter" year="1990">
